&lt;/h2>&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://yutianqaq.github.io/hack-tools/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>HackTools&lt;/a> &lt;a class="link" href="https://gist.github.com/yutianqaq" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
